Class MakeAntLibs

java.lang.Object
  mkr.Build
      mkr.TargetBuild
          mkr.MethodTargetBuild
              MakeAntLibs

public class MakeAntLibs
extends MethodTargetBuild

A build script that generates the ant task facades. The build targets are:

doc
Generates facade class source files
sources
Extracts Ant sources from the zip file
clean
Deletes Ant sources and facades
tidy
Deletes extracted Ant sources
classes
Compiles facade sources
lib
Archives facade sources and class files into a jar

Author:
gilesjb
